@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@projectId = 69c1332bbfc3d21bbfaef099
@repoUrl = https://github.com/expressjs/express

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Simulate Load Without Project Context
POST {{baseUrl}}/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "users": 250
}

### Simulate Load With Project Context
POST {{baseUrl}}/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "users": 500,
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}"
}

### Analyze Repository Using GitHub URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/analyze-repo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repoUrl": "{{repoUrl}}"
}

### Analyze Repository Using Zip Upload
# Update the file path before running this request.
POST {{baseUrl}}/analyze-repo
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ProjectCarsBoundary

--ProjectCarsBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="zipFile"; filename="sample-project.zip"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./tmp/sample-project.zip
--ProjectCarsBoundary--

### Get Architecture By Project ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/architecture/{{projectId}}

### Get Analysis Report By Project ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/analysis/{{projectId}}

### Get Car View By Project ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/car-view/{{projectId}}

### Invalid Simulation Request Example
POST {{baseUrl}}/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "users": 0
}

### Invalid Project ID Example
GET {{baseUrl}}/architecture/invalid-project-id
